name: The creation of venus
description: While he served jaba and my body slept, I could visualize the Creation of the beautiful Venus, I saw how my mind painted her body and between spasms it responded to the excitement of seeing it exist, it was something strange because it is different from how it is described in the books ancient. It has a black hole in its head which is the sustenance of its body. He is here to teach me something and I am intrigued by his visit.
